Keep in mind that this earth is very old, and only a very small part of that timeline is somewhat documented , erosion and plate tectonics among other things might have completely destroyed cultures much older than you can conceive of. Also what makes you so sure that an alien race would be your size, have your ambitions, the need to "invade" , there are life forms and civilizations at different scales.
